  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "IMF seeking certification",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The International Monetary Fund (IMF) said it expected adequate guarantees from the creditors during the visit of an IMF delegation to Sri Lanka.",
        "The International Monetary Fund has announced a visit to Sri Lanka to broker a staff-level agreement to introduce an aid package to tackle the economic crisis Sri Lanka is facing.",
        "Reuters news service reported that IMF staff will visit Sri Lanka from August 24 to 31.",
        "It has been reported that a certificate obtained from the creditor regarding Sri Lanka's debt restructuring is necessary to provide the facilities of the International Monetary Fund. (a)"
      ],
